&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Server-side/Django/skeleton_website#running_the_website">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Server-side/Django/skeleton_website#running_the_website&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>